import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' const UserGoalCard = ({ goalCard: { actualWeight, goalWeight, height, kcal, trainingRate } }) => { return (

Actual weight: {actualWeight}

Goal weight: {goalWeight}

Height: {height ? height : ''}

Kcal: {kcal ? kcal : ''}

Trainings per week: {trainingRate ? trainingRate : ''}

) } UserGoalCard.propTypes = { goalCard: PropTypes.array.isRequired, } export default UserGoalCard
